::Striker::

Striker looks at Xiane as the bot walks up to him, raising an eyebrow at the 
bot's manner of speach. He looks at Hot Rod, a questioning look in his eyes. 
Looking back to Xiane, Striker nods.

"We're gonna reinforce the walls for now. You can help if you want."

He recieves the transmission from Primal. "What's going on, Primal?" he 
replies, wondering what could be wrong this time.
